ingredients_text: Sugar glucose syrup; treacle; maize starch; _wheat flour_; liquorice extract (3% content in the liquorice pieces); dextrose; gelatine; fruit and plant concentrates: safflower, spirulina, apple, carrot, bilberry, elderberry, blackcurrant, orange, kiwi, lemon, aronia, mango, passion fruit, radish, sweet potato, hibiscus, grape; invert sugar syrup; elderberry extract; ammonium chloride; salt; flavouring; acid: citric acid; caramelised sugar syrup; colours: curar carmine, vegetable carbon; anti-cacking agent: talc; palm oil; glazing agents: beeswax white and yellow, carnauba wax; preservative: sorbic acid.
